            Currently, Nepal is facing a huge humanitarian crisis due to economic blockade at the southern custom points. There is a complete shortage of fuel.  The fuel crisis has made the lives of the people of Nepal very hard.  People from Kathmandu are forced to buy wood to cook food due to the lack of the cooking gas/Liquified Petroleum Gas (LPG) cylinders.
